LTE518 need to add specific QCI as default bearer
1) In the configuration file (WTS is in CONFIGURING state) -- configure specific QCI
exec("set_qci qci=129 gbr=no priority=2 delay=100")
exec("set_qci qci=130 gbr=no priority=3 delay=100")
exec("set_qci qci=132 gbr=no priority=4 delay=100")
exec("set_qci qci=133 gbr=no priority=5 delay=100")
this need to change /opt/iphy/latest/**.lua，need to add "set_qci qci=129; qci=130;qci=132;qci=133" total 4 specific QCI. 2) You describe the bearer, that refers to this particular qci:
for i=5,8 do
if(i==5) then -- default bearer id, QCI =5
exec('set_bearer id='..i.. ' ue='..ue_index.. ' trf_type=internal'.. ' default=on'.. ' qci='..i.. ' ip='..ue_ip)
elseif (i==6) then
exec('set_bearer id='..i.. ' ue='..ue_index.. ' default=off'.. ' qci='..i+124)
else-- Non-default bearer, QCI=6,7,8
exec('set_bearer id='..i.. ' ue='..ue_index.. ' default=off'.. ' qci='..i+125)
end
configure qci132 as default bearer, qci133 as dedicated bearer configure qci129 as default bearer, qci130 as dedicated bearer 3) EGATE>start 4) EGATE>bearer_add ue=1 id=5 …
